raw_text = "~ start
#12pm noon around
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Paige: Yoohooooo
Paige: Heeellooo
Player: Hi
Paige: I'm told you're my photographer today
Paige: Good, I'm getting dressed right now
Paige: img: paige/4
Paige: 😉
Player: Uhh I'm confused 😅
Paige: What's there to be confused about silly
Player: Well, we're supposed to go over photography foundations right?
Paige: Ugh, don't be so hung up on that
Paige: We'll improvise... a lot 😜
Paige: img: paige/5
Paige: Ok fine we'll do that too
Paige: But you're gonna take some pictures of me 🫰
Player: That wasn't what we said in the group chat 😆
Paige: Oh that
Paige: Yeah I saw those messages and went back to my beauty sleep 💅
Player: It was noontime 😳
Paige: Monday noon is in the middle of prime beauty sleep time, dontcha know anything? 🤣
Paige: Anyway
Paige: That Naomi girl is such a boor with all this scheduling and boring events
Paige: How can a girl like her be so pretty yet so... 🥱🥱🥱
Paige: Don't you think girl's need to be fun, outgoing and free? 🤭
- Maybe, yeah [#blueheart]
	set Story.blue_heart += 1
	Player: Maybe, yeah
	Paige: Great! Now we've established the obvious 😋😋
- I like Naomi how she is
	Player: I like Naomi how she is
	Paige: Ugh not you toooo 💀💀💀
Paige: Anyway hurry up
Paige: I have to hang out with a girlfriend in an hour and I want to dress up for the occassion
Paige: And I need to do my nails
Paige: And go shopping for some new shoes
Paige: Oh and this new outfit I ordered is arriving today, so you're gonna carry them for me right? 😇
Player: Wha- hold on 😵‍💫
Player: You want me to just follow you around all day?
Paige: Duh
Paige: The Sorority had so many boys like that 😇
- Sure I guess I can
	Player: Sure I guess I can
	Paige: Awwh that's sweet 🥺
	Paige: Great! So while you're at it, you can pick up my groceries too
	Player: 😫
	Paige: I'll send you the list rn
	Player: Hold up 😄
- Ehh do I have to? 😫
	Player: Ehh do I have to? 😫
	Paige: Hmph, yes you do 😠
	Paige: Can you imagine me carrying all those bags? 🥺 With my delicate arms? 😭
	Paige: I'm built like a flower, not a brick 😘
	Player: 😒
Player: We should really get the lessons out of the way
Paige: Alriiiight I am ready
Paige: I sent you my location
Player: Wow, you live nearby
Paige: Well duh, I'm not in the Sorority anymore so no more fancy housing for me
Paige: Anyway, I'm sooo done with those bitches 🙄
Paige: They think they can tell me what to do 🤏 squish
Paige: And I don't care if that means I have to hang out with people like you
Player: People like me? 😅
Paige: Like, no offense of course darling 🥰 I'm sure you're lovely... in your own way
Paige: But hellooo, you coming or what?
Paige: You sure do like to keep a girl waiting
Player: Alright I'm on my way 😅
do advance_time(4, 3)
Paige: Omg we forgot to check the outlets for sales on handbags 😭
Player: I don't know if I'll be feeling my shoulders for the rest of the week 😵
Paige: img: paige/6
Player: Lol I couldn't even see where I was going
Paige: I'll admit that it was cute to see you push yourself so hard for me
Paige: 🤭
Player: 😅
Player: I wish we had gotten through the assigned work though
Paige: Oh please, we had so much more fun
Paige: Besides I already told Naomi we did it 😉
Player: You did what...? 😵‍💫
Paige: Don't be such a worry worm LOL
Paige: If anything happens, I'll just take the blame
Paige: And then I'll do this
Paige: img: paige/7
Paige: And all my problems are solved 😇
Paige: Could you refuse this face?
- No 😣 [#blueheart]
	set Story.blue_heart += 1
	Player: No 😣
	Paige: Of course not 😘
- 😒
	Player: 😒
	Paige: Well it usually works on kind people 😤
Paige: Send me the pics already, will ya? 🫵 poke
Paige: I liked how they came out sooo hurry up 😝
Player: Alright
Player: img: paige/8
Paige: Omg this is like totally one of the BEST pics of me I've ever seen
Paige: I mean I'm sure I'll have a better one next week but rn its my fav 🤭 
Player: It only took like 60 attempts until you were satisfied
Paige: What do you expect, the wind kept blowing my hair into my mouth 😭
Paige: Okay, what about the other one, with my friend
Player: img: paige/9
if Story.yellow_heart > 0:
	Player: She seems familiar
	Paige: Nooo offense buuut
	Paige: I doubt you'd know the Sorority girls personally but you might have seen her around
Paige: She's the sweetest angel ever y'know
Paige: When the Sorority turned their backs on me, she never did 😇
if Story.blue_heart >= 2:	
	Paige: But I still can't believe she thought you were my new boyfriend LOL 😭
	Player: She did? 😆
	Paige: Yuhu, she was all giggly and whispering to me that I had quite the catch and I was all like BABE NO 😭
	Paige: Seriously... that girl 😏
Paige: Well? 
Paige: Aren't you glad you had the honor of going out with me? 😘
- I guess it was nice [#blueheart]
	set Story.blue_heart += 1
	Player: I guess it was nice
	Paige: Really? 🤩
	Paige: So I can rely on you for next time too? 😌
	Player: Maybe once my arms are back in their sockets
	Paige: Oh please, you carried everything easily 😘
- It was... something 😅
	Player: It was... something
	Paige: I can't force you to have a good time I guess 🙄
if Story.blue_heart >= 3:	
	Paige: Since I'm not in the Sorority anymore, I'll need my own personal pocket boy 😘
	Paige: You'll have to be on call anytime I need you for shopping
	Paige: Pick up my packages, sort my mail, do my groceries and laundry, buy my make up, check sales for me
	Paige: Aaaand run some errands for me on campus
	Paige: 🤝
	Player: That's a lot of stuff 😱
	Paige: 🤭
	Paige: Oh and one last thing
	Player: 😩
	Paige: It's been just a little boring since I moved to this area
	Paige: My only friend lives on the other campus sooo
	Paige: It's just a teensy bit lonely
	Paige: If you'll keep a girl company, that'd be nice
	Paige: img: paige/10
	Player: Yeah, sure
	Player: I can do that
	Paige: GREAT 😍
	Paige: So tomorrow is usually my laundry day
	Paige: You can come by around 4pm to pick it up and return it at night
	Player: 🥲
	Paige: Cya 😘
else:
	Paige: Well, it's been real, toodles!
	Paige: Maybe I'll see you around in club
	Player: Bye Paige
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
